WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.988 align:middle line:90%
[LOGO SOUND]

00:00:02.988 --> 00:00:04.482 align:middle line:90%


00:00:04.482 --> 00:00:07.470 align:middle line:90%
[LOGO MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:07.470 --> 00:00:16.434 align:middle line:90%


00:00:16.434 --> 00:00:19.422 align:middle line:90%
